# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:15
translate portuguese brandis1_a62517a3:

    # fd "I'm from right here actually. Born and raised in Skyhill."
    fd "Na verdade, sou daqui. Nasci e cresci em Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:16
translate portuguese brandis1_dfe249fc:

    # pc "Really? Did we go to school together?"
    pc "A sério? Andámos na escola juntos?"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:17
translate portuguese brandis1_adbdf97b:

    # fd "I was homeschooled."
    fd "Fui educada em casa."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:18
translate portuguese brandis1_cc5944f4:

    # pc "And you've lived here all your life?"
    pc "E viveste aqui toda a tua vida?"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:19
translate portuguese brandis1_77760cf3:

    # fd "I left Skyhill for a few years with my parents, but last year when I had enough money to support myself, I moved back."
    fd "Saí de Skyhill por alguns anos com os meus pais, mas no ano passado, quando já tinha dinheiro suficiente para me sustentar, voltei."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:20
translate portuguese brandis1_cebbbeda:

    # pc "Why'd you move back?"
    pc "Porque é que voltaste?"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:22
translate portuguese brandis1_01768677:

    # fd "I don't know."
    fd "Não sei."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:24
translate portuguese brandis1_496f7e0e:

    # fd "I traveled with my parents to a lot of different places, but there's just something about Skyhill that I love."
    fd "Viajei com os meus pais para muitos lugares diferentes, mas há algo em Skyhill que adoro."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:25
translate portuguese brandis1_1049c078:

    # fd "Nowhere else felt like home to me."
    fd "Nenhum outro lugar me fez sentir em casa."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:27
translate portuguese brandis1_b803d47d:

    # fd "Kind of weird I guess, huh?"
    fd "É um pouco estranho, acho eu, não é?"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:28
translate portuguese brandis1_3f5bf1e9:

    # pc "No, I get it."
    pc "Não, eu entendo."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:29
translate portuguese brandis1_381b77b4:

    # pc "For a long time I just wanted to get away from here, but more and more I'm finding it difficult to imagine leaving."
    pc "Durante muito tempo, só queria ir embora daqui, mas cada vez mais acho difícil imaginar partir."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:31
translate portuguese brandis1_892eafa0:

    # fd "Yeah that's how I feel too."
    fd "Sim, também me sinto assim."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:32
translate portuguese brandis1_6b9b4a38:

    # fd "Like, I'd love to travel all over, but then I'd want to eventually come back home to Skyhill."
    fd "Tipo, adoraria viajar por todo o lado, mas depois acabaria por querer voltar para casa, para Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:33
translate portuguese brandis1_0d233edf:

    # fd "It's kind of strange, but even the food tastes better here for some reason."
    fd "É um pouco estranho, mas até a comida sabe melhor aqui, por alguma razão."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:34
translate portuguese brandis1_2643738c:

    # pc "I don't know about that."
    pc "Não sei se é verdade."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:36
translate portuguese brandis1_89b010bc:

    # fd "It does!"
    fd "Sabe mesmo!"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandis1.rpy:37
translate portuguese brandis1_25cec234:

    # fd "Trust me, I'm a professional."
    fd "Acredita em mim, sou um profissional."

